 -t wh-n th- g-ntl-m-n -nt-r-d,  -n- w-s n- l-ng-r th- f-rst -bj-ct;
 -ss  -ngl-y's -y-s w-r- -nst-ntly t-rn-d t-w-rd  -rcy, -nd sh- h-d
