“ - m-ch th- b-tt-r. - h-p- th-y w-ll n-t m--t -t -ll.  -t d--s n-t  -n-
c-rr-sp-nd w-th h-s s-st-r? _ h-_ w-ll n-t b- -bl- t- h-lp c-ll-ng.”

“ h- w-ll dr-p th- -cq---nt-nc- -nt-r-ly.”

 -t -n sp-t- -f th- c-rt--nty -n wh-ch -l-z-b-th -ff-ct-d t- pl-c- th-s
