 h-n th- p-rty br-k- -p,  yd-- r-t-rn-d w-th  rs.  -rst-r t-  -ryt-n,
fr-m wh-nc- th-y w-r- t- s-t --t --rly th- n-xt m-rn-ng.  h- s-p-r-t--n
