s-mm-r.

“ -r my -wn p-rt,” sh- r-j--n-d, “- m-st c-nf-ss th-t - n-v-r c--ld
s-- -ny b---ty -n h-r.  -r f-c- -s t-- th-n; h-r c-mpl-x--n h-s n-
